import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { MDBContainer, MDBBtn, MDBModal, MDBModalBody, MDBModalHeader, MDBModalFooter, MDBRow, MDBCol, MDBInput } from 'mdbreact';

class ViewOrderModal extends Component {
    state = {
        modalShow: false,
        orderId: ''
    }

    toggle = () => {
        this.setState({
            modalShow: !this.state.modalShow,

        });
    }
    fetchData = (id) => {

        fetch('/getSpecificOrder/')
            .then((res) => res.json())
            .then((json) => {
                console.log(json)
                this.toggle();
            })
            .catch((error) => console.log(error))
    }

    render() {
        // console.log(this.state.orderId);

        return (
            <MDBContainer>
                <MDBModal isOpen={this.state.modalShow} toggle={this.toggle} size='lg' centered>
                    <MDBModalHeader toggle={this.toggle}>Order details</MDBModalHeader>
                    <MDBModalBody>
                        <MDBRow center>
                            <MDBCol md="9" className='m-0 p-0'>
                                <MDBRow center className='m-0 p-0' >
                                    <MDBCol sm='6' className='m-0'>
                                        <MDBInput value={this.state.orderTotal} label="Total" hint="Total" disabled className='m-0' style={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }} />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                    <MDBCol sm='6' className='m-0'>
                                        <MDBInput value={this.state.totalValueAdded} className='m-0' style={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }} label="Total value added" hint="Total value added" disabled />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                </MDBRow>
                                <MDBRow center className='m-0 p-0' >
                                    <MDBCol sm='4' className='m-0 ' >
                                        <MDBInput value={this.state.orderId} label="Id" outline disabled className='mt-0 mb-0' />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                    <MDBCol md='4' className=' ' middle >
                                        <MDBInput outline label='Source' disabled />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                    <MDBCol md='4' className='m-0 ' middle >
                                        <MDBInput outline label='Status' disabled />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                </MDBRow>
                                <MDBRow center className='m-0 p-0' >
                                    <MDBCol sm='4' className='m-0 '>
                                        <MDBInput label="Tracking Id" value={this.state.orderTracking} outline className='m-0' disabled />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                    <MDBCol sm='8' className='m-0 '>
                                        <MDBInput label="Note" value={this.state.orderNote} outline className='m-0' disabled />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                </MDBRow>
                                <MDBRow className='m-0 p-0' end>
                                    <MDBCol sm='12' className='m-0 p-0' bottom >
                                        <label style={{ fontWeight: 'bold', textAlign: 'left' }}>Customer:</label>
                                    </MDBCol>
                                </MDBRow>
                                <MDBRow className='m-0 p-0'>
                                    <MDBCol sm='3' className='m-0'>
                                        <MDBInput value={this.state.cName} className='m-0' label="Name" outline disabled />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                    <MDBCol sm='3' className='m-0'>
                                        <MDBInput value={this.state.cContact} className='m-0' label="Contact" outline disabled />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                    <MDBCol sm='6' className='m-0'>
                                        <MDBInput value={this.state.cAddress} className='m-0' label="Address" outline disabled />
                                    </MDBCol>

                                </MDBRow>
                                <MDBRow className='m-0 p-0' end>
                                    <MDBCol sm='12' className='m-0 p-0' bottom >
                                        <label style={{ fontWeight: 'bold', textAlign: 'left' }}>Products:</label>
                                    </MDBCol>
                                </MDBRow>



                            </MDBCol>
                        </MDBRow>
                    </MDBModalBody>
                    <MDBModalFooter>
                        <MDBBtn color="secondary" onClick={this.toggle}>Close</MDBBtn>
                    </MDBModalFooter>
                </MDBModal>
            </MDBContainer>
        );
    }
}

export default ViewOrderModal;
